text: Workum (, ) is a city located in the municipality of Súdwest-Fryslân in Friesland, Netherlands. It received city rights in 1374. It is one of the eleven cities of Friesland. It had a population of 4,435 in January 2017. ==References== Category:Cities in Friesland Category:Súdwest-Fryslân
title: Workum
